Package org.frc2851.crevolib.motion

Class MotionProfileExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.frc2851.crevolib.motion.MotionProfileExecutor
  • public class MotionProfileExecutor
extends java.lang.Object
    MotionProfileExecutor: A class which takes in a file and a talon and executes a motion profile This class takes in a pathfinder csv file, converts it to a format readable by a TalonSRX, and handles running the motion profile on the Talon. Unit Conversions: - Pathfinder Unit (Velocity) (f/s) - CTRE Unit (Velocity) (avg_counts/100ms)
